sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Envoy as Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS Terminate
    participant EF as EnvoyFilter<br/>ext_authz
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth/OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Component<br/>(via HTTPRoute)

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 1: Platform Ingress Authentication (Gateway API)

    Client->>Router: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>No initial auth
    Router->>Envoy: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS termination
    Envoy->>EF: ext_authz check
    EF->>AuthProxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token check
    AuthProxy->>OAuth: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>OAuth2 client credentials
    OAuth-->>AuthProxy: Token validation response
    AuthProxy->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>TokenReview (SA token)
    K8sAPI-->>AuthProxy: TokenReview result
    AuthProxy-->>EF: Auth decision
    EF-->>Envoy: ext_authz response
    Envoy->>Upstream: Forward request<br/>Forwarded auth headers
    Upstream-->>Envoy: Response
    Envoy-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 2: Component Deployment via DSC

    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant Webhook as DSC Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
    participant CompCtrl as Component Controller
    participant Manifests as Kustomize Manifests<br/>/opt/manifests-template

    Admin->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Bearer Token (kubeconfig)<br/>Create/Update DSC
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: HTTPS/9443<br/>mTLS (API server cert)<br/>Admission Review
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit/Reject
    K8sAPI-->>Admin: DSC created/updated
    K8sAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch notification
    DSCCtrl->>DSCCtrl: Create Component CR<br/>(e.g., Dashboard)
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>SA Bearer Token<br/>Create Component CR
    K8sAPI->>CompCtrl: Watch notification
    CompCtrl->>Manifests: Read manifests<br/>(filesystem)
    CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>SA Bearer Token<br/>Apply manifests

    Note over Client,Upstream: Flow 3: Monitoring Metrics Collection

    participant OTelCol as OTel Collector<br/>(TargetAllocator)
    participant Pods as Component Pods<br/>(scrape=true)
    participant MonStack as MonitoringStack<br/>(Prometheus)
    participant Thanos as ThanosQuerier<br/>10901/TCP gRPC
    participant NSProxy as Namespace Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTPS

    OTelCol->>Pods: HTTP (varies)<br/>Scrape metrics
    Pods-->>OTelCol: Metrics data
    OTelCol->>MonStack: OTLP HTTP/4318<br/>TLS
    Thanos->>MonStack: gRPC/10901<br/>TLS<br/>Federated query
    Client->>NSProxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Bearer Token
    NSProxy->>Prom: HTTPS/9090<br/>TLS (service-CA)
    Prom-->>NSProxy: Metrics response
    NSProxy-->>Client: Authorized metrics
